# User-uploaded content (IMPORTANT: User-generated files)
# Avatars - ignore all user-uploaded avatar files
**/wwwroot/images/avatars/*
!**/wwwroot/images/avatars/.gitkeep

# Reviews - ignore all review images (including subdirectories by reviewId)
**/wwwroot/images/reviews/**
!**/wwwroot/images/reviews/.gitkeep

# Product images - ignore admin-uploaded product images (product_*.jpg pattern)
# But keep static/default product images
**/wwwroot/images/products/product_*.jpg
**/wwwroot/images/products/product_*.png
